<div class="com-share" data-id="5787" data-title="《华人解开世纪数学难题？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/5787/medium/5787.jpg?1436690220" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/5787.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
